org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.model
Class RegisterForAbrc

java.lang.Object
  org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.model.RegisterForAbrc
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class RegisterForAbrc
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

A Faces Managed Bean that models the registration feature for ABRC ABRC requires these elements: Right now we are collecting:

  • First name
  • Last name
  • Email
  • Phone
  • Job Title
  • Billing Address (lab address)
  • Shipping Address (person address)
  • Username
  • Password
  • Lab Name ("School name" because this is for teachers buying education kits from TAIR from a location external to TAIR)

Author:
Robert J. Muller
